                            <comment id="17723738" author="garydgregory" created="Wed, 17 May 2023 21:35:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes and no. I initially created it in tests because it was only used for tests and forgot to move it to the main source tree after realizing that it could be generally useful. &lt;del&gt;I&apos;ll fix that for the next release.&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;BUT, we already have a &lt;tt&gt;CharSequenceInputStream&lt;/tt&gt;, so we do not need a &lt;tt&gt;StringInputStream&lt;/tt&gt;! So it&apos;s now gone in git master!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
